imdb.plot outline: In "Auf und davon", we show the enthralling stories of young people who follow their hearts. Our heroines manage to overcome geographical and personal boundaries. At first glance, "Auf und davon" seems to be an adventure-format, but it contains much more: In essence, it focuses on the moving causes of our protagonists, their motivations, their desires, their fears and moments of success.
imdb.title: Auf und davon - Mein Auslandstagebuch
